info.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 09 at 9:08PM PST until January 10 at 4:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM PST TUESDAY... * WHAT...South winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 60 mph. * WHERE...Ventura County Mountains and Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains. * WHEN...Until 4 PM PST Tuesday. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds may blow down trees and power lines, possibly causing power outages. Travel will be difficult, especially for drivers of high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around large trees. If possible, stay in your home during the windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.
